          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">UI/UX Design</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          User-centered design solutions that combine aesthetics with functionality to create engaging experiences.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
